    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the garlic and ginger are fragrant, add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until toasted</p><p>Add the <strong>gochujang</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and cook for 2-3 min</p><p>Add the <strong>halved white pak choi bases </strong>and cook for 3-4 min further or until tender</p>",
