    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once tender, drain, then add your <strong>king prawns </strong>to the pot and increase the heat to medium-high, cook for 4-5 min or until pink and cooked through</p><p>Add the <strong>pak choi leaves </strong>and cook for 1 min or until wilted – this is your <strong>Korean-style king prawn jjam-pong soup</strong></p>",
